headline.print_headline: Organizers: Russian Grand Prix to Go Ahead
headline.main: Organizers: Russian Grand Prix to Go Ahead

lead_paragraph: Organizers insist Russia's first Formula One Grand Prix will go ahead as planned despite an airliner being shot down in the conflict zone in eastern Ukraine.
